{"tid":2300033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息指毀壞整個輕鐵站便無法以警司警誡方式處理","createTime":"2020-11-25T07:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T09:11:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a10bf639f0ca9e650bc2a024afb812a474635992","tid":2300033,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T07:58:09.000Z","msg":"《施政報告》中提到，在「修例風波」中被捕的18歲以下有悔意而非涉及嚴重罪行的被捕人士，警方願意視乎情況考慮採取讓其改過自新的措施，例如警司警誡等。<br />\n<br />\n政府消息人士說，在「修例風波」中被檢控的2300多人中，當中429人屬於18歲以下，其中19宗案件已用警司警誡方式處理，涉及刑事毀壞、公眾地方行為不檢。消息人士說，如以警司警誡方式處理，前提是該名未成年人士，必須認罪、有悔意及所犯罪行性質輕微。<br />\n<br />\n對於刑事毀壞是否屬輕微罪行，消息人士說，要視乎嚴重程度，舉例如涉及毀壞整個輕鐵站，便無法以警司警誡方式處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561886-20201125.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561886-20201125.htm&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwqGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=4eae9e99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1561886-20201125.htm&h=7e090eac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1561886-20201125.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ae2bd1cefdf349e917a59c8d1fec5a52323ee0cf","tid":2300033,"uid":21545,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:06:06.000Z","msg":"點樣可以破壞成個輕鐵站<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351bfe8a3b86e9bf833687f3308f4c5992b6fd15","tid":2300033,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae2bd1cefdf349e917a59c8d1fec5a52323ee0cf","tid":2300033,"uid":21545,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:06:06.000Z","msg":"點樣可以破壞成個輕鐵站<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T08:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmo